            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} U _ {x, N} | u _ {s} \\rangle = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {r}} \\sum_ {k = 0} ^ {r - 1} \\exp \\left[ \\frac {- 2 \\pi i s k}{r} \\right] | x ^ {k + 1} \\bmod N \\rangle \\\\ = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {r}} \\sum_ {k = 1} ^ {r} \\exp \\left[ \\frac {- 2 \\pi i s (k - 1)}{r} \\right] | x ^ {k} \\bmod {\\mathrm{N}} \\rangle \\\\ = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {r}} \\sum_ {k = 0} ^ {r - 1} \\exp \\left[ \\frac {- 2 \\pi i s (k - 1)}{r} \\right] | x ^ {k} \\bmod \\mathrm{N} \\rangle \\\\ = \\exp \\left[ \\frac {2 \\pi i s}{r} \\right] \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {r}} \\sum_ {k = 0} ^ {r - 1} \\exp \\left[ \\frac {- 2 \\pi i s k}{r} \\right] | x ^ {k} \\bmod N \\rangle \\\\ = \\exp \\left[ \\frac {2 \\pi i s}{r} \\right] | u _ {s} \\rangle \\tag {22.4} \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
